extends layout

block content
  h1 Timestamp Microservice
  blockquote User stories:
    ol
      li I can pass a string as a parameter, and it will check to see whether that string contains either a unix timestamp or a natural language date (example: February 02, 2018)
      li If it does, it returns both the Unix timestamp and the natural language form of that date.
      li If it does not contain a date or Unix timestamp, it returns null for those properties. 
  p.red Input Example
  a localhost:3000/February 02, 2018
  br
  a localhost:3000/1517526000
  p.red Output Example JSON
  code {"unix":"1517526000", "time":"February 02, 2018"}
  
